spp1_128x128x8.bin contains the 1-spp SCRAMBLING_TILE bytes from
Jasper Bekkers' MIT-licensed blue-noise-sampler repository at commit
b1720f637a3580c8711580873dcf84cce82f6504.

https://github.com/Jasper-Bekkers/blue-noise-sampler

The tables implement the sampler described by Eric Heitz, Laurent Belcour,
Victor Ostromoukhov, David Coeurjolly, and Jean-Claude Iehl in "A
Low-Discrepancy Sampler that Distributes Monte Carlo Errors as a Blue Noise
in Screen Space" (SIGGRAPH 2019).
